{"word":"H914 - בָּדַל - bâdal - baw-dal' - Difference","slug":"H914","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּדַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bâdal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>baw-dal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Difference"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D3;&#x05DC; - ba&#x0302;dal</b> - <i>baw-dal'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>divide</i> (in various senses literally or figuratively, <i>separate</i>, <i>distinguish</i>, <i>differ</i>, <i>select</i>, etc.): - (make, put) difference, divide (asunder), (make) separate (self, -ation), sever (out), X utterly."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3995\">H3995</a>, <a href=\"#/H913\">H913</a>, <a href=\"#/H915\">H915</a>, <a href=\"#/H916\">H916</a>, <a href=\"#/H917\">H917</a>"}]}